<p class="ql-align-justify">茫茫林海，一望无边</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">内蒙古拥有着一份珍贵的自然资源</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">3.92亿亩的森林面积居全国首位</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">丛林密布的大兴安岭</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">绵延千里的阴山</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">神奇瑰丽的贺兰山</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">是内蒙古大地坚实的嵴梁</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">更是内蒙古森林的家园</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200917/5ab575d5a84c457cb1f5c534abc3a805.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">春天的大森林</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">是生命的竞技场</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">遍地充满了勃勃生机</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">处处涌动着生命的欲望</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">夏天的大森林茂密而又喧闹</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">万物肆意生长</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">尽情展现挺拔英姿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200917/a5f0ed5a7b514bd3b31ec3d35dccc93a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
