<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-justify">秋天的大森林浓墨重彩</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">五彩斑斓充满艺术氛围</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200917/f6e6f9581e36499ead565a6e938fe547.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">冬季的大森林万籁俱寂</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">冰凌和白雪勾勒出冬日恋歌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200917/7a5384a0cfc545febb5d91c981609aff.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">大森林看似茂密杂乱</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">实则秩序井然</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">高大的乔木傲然挺立</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">拼命将身躯伸向云天</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">灌木铺展在乔木的下面</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">草本植物悠然自得</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">菌类苔藓占据着林下最底层</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">护持着土壤和林木的根基</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">动物们在森林中繁衍生息</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200917/c49387a9276c4026a26def5454dcc947.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">那阵阵的松涛</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">那悦耳的鸟鸣</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">那深谷下潺潺的溪流</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">真想置身其间尽享芬芳</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">快些走上高高的山巅</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">亲切地问候</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">大森林!</p>
